      <title>即使在上涨 350% 后，Novo 的交易价格仍比礼来公司大幅折扣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/novo-trades-at-hefty-discount-to-lilly-even-after-350-rally</link>
